properties.name: BASELINESTANDARD
properties.description: Select Baseline (Standard) to use a format recognized by most web browsers.

properties.name: BASELINEOPTIMIZED
properties.description: Select Baseline Optimized for optimized color and a slightly smaller file size. Not supported by all web browsers.

properties.name: PROGRESSIVE
properties.description: Select Progressive to display a series of increasingly detailed scans (you specify how many in ProgressiveScan) as the image downloads. Not supported by all web browsers.
